{"tid":1922864,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"淡友預上大熊，星期六睇樓","createTime":"2020-03-12T21:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T06:43:26.000Z","uid":292534,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05b1b61729e6448ea1ab8310619b92e09e94ae76","tid":1922864,"uid":292534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XtKgMac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtKgMac.jpg&h=7d87598b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深信天理循環，潮汐漲退，年頭開始做淡友 <br />\n重鎚熊仔，亦都係樓市淡友 ，<br />\n一直未買 估唔到一鋪幫我贏到首期+稅<br />\n星期六去睇樓（未買住）因為睇返往續股市大冧後6個月 樓市必冧 ，所以睇定心儀盤9月去殺價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c2f047d6045bde3caa217b65ef8a11dddb950a","tid":1922864,"uid":320714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"489bd4c5ad6d84b413655171175e71270e4dd1d3","tid":1922864,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:27:04.000Z","msg":"記住好食，唔好貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e45e5907e7016138d3344397965d52a6b0187c8","tid":1922864,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:30:19.000Z","msg":"恭喜<br />\n今朝又贏錢錢"},{"pid":"b9c75216bc13ac938e6b320b92a3ce9fdb5c295d","tid":1922864,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:31:13.000Z","msg":"我9萬期權倉<br />\n聽朝開市預計封20個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 仲差緊銀行錢"},{"pid":"9ae0f37d84d8d7dc7eef022759dc0965996dfdfe","tid":1922864,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9c75216bc13ac938e6b320b92a3ce9fdb5c295d","tid":1922864,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T21:31:13.0